{"title":"文字测试","uid":"85d7ce1242f473be51ae344a6b76042d","slug":"文字测试","date":"2021-10-02T16:36:19.000Z","updated":"2021-10-04T11:08:47.760Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/文字测试.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/bb34eceb7dd20bb316c793ce0ac2993e16333456145719/0.jpg","content":"<div class='mdfont'>这是上篇文章的彩色文字练习</div>\n\n<div class='hidden'>这是一段测试文字，不会自适应</div>\n\n<p><hidden>这是自适应长文字测试</hidden></p>\n<p><hidden>短文字</hidden></p>\n<hr>\n\n<h2 id=\"嘿，今天又看上哪个样式了？？？\"><a href=\"#嘿，今天又看上哪个样式了？？？\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"嘿，今天又看上哪个样式了？？？\"></a>嘿，今天又看上哪个样式了？？？</h2><p>我学前端的兴趣之一是别人做的网页太好看了。我也想获得此能力！<br>那么，在建站的第140天，我又看上了一款样式。</p>\n<p>之前是看中了<a href=\"https://www.heson10.com/\">黑石博客</a>的鼠标点击特效，看这篇文章：<a href=\"http://huakai.site/2021/09/30/shubiaotexiao/\">http://huakai.site/2021/09/30/shubiaotexiao/</a></p>\n<p>今天看上了白洛嘉的博客的鼠标悬浮显示文字。</p>\n<p>详见：<a href=\"https://phenol-phthalein.info/about/\">单向好友白洛嘉的博客</a></p>\n<p>下面记录我ba下样式的过程，<br>首先，按调试器看他的代码样式，取消里面的参数，看那个参数取消了样式跟着取消了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/10/03/wenziceshi/1.png\"></p>\n<p>嗯，发现相关代码：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.yue del</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">text-decoration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token important\">!important</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> .2s <span class=\"token function\">cubic-bezier</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>.25<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.46<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.45<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.94<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> color<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.2s <span class=\"token function\">cubic-bezier</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>.25<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.46<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.45<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.94<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> background<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> .2s <span class=\"token function\">cubic-bezier</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>.25<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.46<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.45<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.94<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> color<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.2s <span class=\"token function\">cubic-bezier</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>.25<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.46<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.45<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.94<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> background\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.yue del *</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> .35s <span class=\"token function\">cubic-bezier</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>.25<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.46<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.45<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.94<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> opacity<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n    <span class=\"token property\">transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> .35s <span class=\"token function\">cubic-bezier</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>.25<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.46<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.45<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.94<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> opacity \n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.yue del:not(:hover)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> transparent<span class=\"token important\">!important</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #000<span class=\"token important\">!important</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.yue del:not(:hover) *</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token important\">!important</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.yue del:not(:hover),.yue del:not(:hover) *</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token important\">!important</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>下面就是移花接木了</p></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>.yue看上去不是好人，删了然后再粘到我的样式表里来。测试，没效果</li>\n<li>然后F12看我的文字是什么在控制</li>\n<li>原来是#articleContent p {}</li>\n<li>替换成#articleContent p del/#articleContent p del 等等等</li>\n<li>OK，成功显示效果</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/10/03/wenziceshi/2.png\"></p>\n<p>但是白洛嘉的是自适应文字长度，我的是一行，而且用法是</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>del<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>文字<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>他是用<code>&lt;del&gt;</code>包裹起来的</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>del</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>这是一段文字<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>del</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>于是，就稍微改动一下,成功自适应文字长度，并且del这个名字不太符合效果，换成了hidden，以后写文章的时候就知道hidden包裹起来的文字是隐藏的.</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>下面是我的样式代码</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">#articleContent p >hidden</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n\t\n    <span class=\"token property\">text-decoration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token important\">!important</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> .2s <span class=\"token function\">cubic-bezier</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>.25<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.46<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.45<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.94<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> color<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.2s <span class=\"token function\">cubic-bezier</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>.25<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.46<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.45<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.94<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> background<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> .2s <span class=\"token function\">cubic-bezier</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>.25<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.46<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.45<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.94<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> color<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.2s <span class=\"token function\">cubic-bezier</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>.25<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.46<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.45<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.94<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> background\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#articleContent p >hidden *</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">-webkit-transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> .35s <span class=\"token function\">cubic-bezier</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>.25<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.46<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.45<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.94<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> opacity<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">transition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> .35s <span class=\"token function\">cubic-bezier</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>.25<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.46<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.45<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>.94<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> opacity\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#articleContent p> hidden:not(:hover)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> transparent<span class=\"token important\">!important</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #000<span class=\"token important\">!important</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#articleContent p > hidden:not(:hover) *</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token important\">!important</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">#articleContent p > hidden:not(:hover),.yue del:not(:hover) *</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token important\">!important</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>那么文章开头的隐藏文字在md中如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>mdfont<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>这是上篇文章的彩色文字练习<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>hidden<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>这是一段测试文字，不会自适应<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>hidden</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>这是自适应长文字测试<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>hidden</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>hidden</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>短文字<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>hidden</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>再看一下显示效果吧</p>\n<div class='hidden'>这是一段测试文字，不会自适应</div>\n\n<p><hidden>这是自适应长文字测试</hidden></p>\n<p><hidden>短文字</hidden></p>\n<h2 id=\"完\"><a href=\"#完\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"完\"></a><center>完</h2><p>oh,shit！<br>手机没效果<br>去大佬那看了一眼正常</p>\n<p>应该是matery主题适配了小屏幕手机样式，之后再改吧，今天又搞到两点，睡觉了 😪</p>\n","text":"这是上篇文章的彩色文字练习 这是一段测试文字，不会自适应 这是自适应长文字测试 短文字 嘿，今天又看上哪个样式了？？？我学前端的兴趣之一是别人做的网页太好看了。我也想获得此能力！那么，在建站的第140天，我又看上了一款样式。 之前是看中了黑石博客的鼠标点击特效，看这篇文章：htt...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.4k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"文章编辑","slug":"文章编辑","count":7,"path":"api/categories/文章编辑.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"文字测试","slug":"文字测试","count":1,"path":"api/tags/文字测试.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class